debug-analysis.expected-log-sequence:
After restart, for a newly changed Odoo ticket, you should see:

[INFO]  "Found 1 recently changed tickets in Odoo"
[INFO]  "Enqueueing ticket for sync"          { ticketId, ticketName, jobId }
[INFO]  "Ticket enqueued successfully"         { ticketId, jobId }
[INFO]  "Worker picked up job"                 { jobId, name: "odoo-to-linear" }
[INFO]  "Processing Odoo ticket → Linear"      { odooId, ticketName }
[INFO]  "Idempotency check passed"
[INFO]  "Ticket mapping lookup complete"        { existingMapping: "none" }
[INFO]  "No existing mapping — creating new issue in Linear"
[INFO]  "Sending create issue request to Linear API"
[INFO]  "Linear API response received"          { linearIssueId }
[INFO]  "Job completed successfully"
